snippet.title: The Mouse Game - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist "The Mouse Game" on Steam now!

The Mouse Game is a hardcore maze game where you play as a mouse that needs to survive various deadly traps in order to secure the cheese. Can you beat all 35 levels?
